ActPilotage Act
SubjectPacific Pilotage Authority's borrowing Limit ** Increase **
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2018-1493 of November 29, 2018; and, (2) fixing the maximum amount of money that can be borrowed at any time by the PACIFIC PILOTAGE AUTHORITY, in Canada or elsewhere, for the purpose of defraying its expenses at $18,900,000.
